This skill bundles `assets/base.css`, the slide engine + design tokens from the
open-design project (design-templates/html-ppt). It is included under its original
MIT license, reproduced below. The theme palettes in `assets/themes.css` follow the
same project's theme set. `runtime.js`, the deck templates and the export scripts are
original Polaris work.

